net.danielmelcer.cheekers.board

Class SoftStack<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.danielmelcer.cheekers.board.SoftStack<T>

  • public class SoftStack<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class manages a stack of a given type. References sufficiently below the top of the stack are placed into SoftReferences. This means that if the JVM runs out of memory, it will start removing items from the stack.

        Parameters:
